OL,6,GEvery so often the BBC shoots itself
OL,7,Gin the foot.  A stupid decision which
OL,8,Gcan be justified on paper backfires.
OL,10,FNo, we're not talking about the
OL,11,Freprieve of the BBC Singers ` a
OL,12,Fwelcome move which will hopefully
OL,13,Flead to a viable future for them.
OL,15,FInstead we are talking about Thursday
OL,16,Fnight's scheduling on BBC One.
OL,18,FThe spin-off programme The Apprentice
OL,19,FYou're Fired was promoted over to BBC
OL,20,FOne, delaying the News at Ten and
OL,21,FQuestion Time by half an hour.
OL,3,CLet's not make a habit of moving BBC
OL,4,COne news programmes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/7
