OL,6,FNow you can see the logic. The spin-
OL,7,Foff programme might appeal to more
OL,8,Fpeople than usual after the final.
OL,10,FAlas, the ratings were still lower
OL,11,Fthan the news would have got. While
OL,12,Fthe ITV News at Ten got a
OL,13,Fsignificantly bigger audience than
OL,14,Fusual.
OL,16,FAdding to the sense of an own goal, a
OL,17,Fwork to rule in the English regions
OL,18,Fover job cuts caused problems.
OL,19,FJournalists whose shift officially
OL,20,Ffinished at 11 (the time of the
OL,21,Fdelayed regional bulletins) could not
OL,22,Fstay back.
OL,3,CLet's not make a habit of moving BBC
OL,4,COne news programmes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
