OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F342A1680193627
OL,6,FSimilarly if a live football match
OL,7,Foverruns, a delay is acceptable.
OL,9,FBut a spin-off from a programme
OL,10,Fshifted over to the main channel for
OL,11,Fthe night?  On a Thursday night?
OL,12,FWhich might have been a busy news day?
OL,14,FIt is time to nip this in the bud.
OL,16,FThe BBC needs to make a clear
OL,17,Fdeclaration of intent and do it fast.
OL,18,FThe News at Ten must only be delayed
OL,19,Fon routine weekdays in the most
OL,20,Fexceptional of circumstances.
OL,3,CLet's not make a habit of moving BBC
OL,4,COne news programmes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
