OL,6,FOtherwise it might as well simply
OL,7,Fcopy ITV and treat the news as a
OL,8,Fmovable feast with all the
OL,9,Fdifficulties that causes.
OL,11,FThere is a certain urgency to this.
OL,13,FUntil now, you could always say that
OL,14,Fsomeone who wanted the news at
OL,15,Fexactly 10pm could simply switch to
OL,16,Fthe News Channel.
OL,18,FBut it now carries less domestic news
OL,19,Fand has to accommodate an
OL,20,Finternational audience.
OL,3,CLet's not make a habit of moving BBC
OL,4,COne news programmes
