OL,6,FThere is a little bit of history
OL,7,Frepeating itself.
OL,9,FDuring the BBC's difficult year of
OL,10,F1984, one of the biggest
OL,11,Fcontroversies concerned the screening
OL,12,Fof the US mini-series The Thorn Birds.
OL,14,FYou might wonder just what was so
OL,15,Fterrible about it. It was a glossy
OL,16,Fand popular series while in those
OL,17,Fdays both BBC One and ITV showed far
OL,18,Fmore imported programmes than today
OL,19,Fwithout comment.
OL,3,CLet's not make a habit of moving BBC
OL,4,COne news programmes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/7
