OL,6,FThe problem was it delayed the Nine
OL,7,Fo'Clock News and Panorama. No doubt
OL,8,Fthis is why it caught the attention
OL,9,Fof politicians.
OL,11,FIt was a massive own goal just when
OL,12,Fthe government of the day was out to
OL,13,Fget the BBC.
OL,15,FDon't let the same thing happen again.
OL,3,CLet's not make a habit of moving BBC
OL,4,COne news programmes
